---
---

<section class="mission section" id="mission">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="mission-header animate-in">
      <span class="section-label">Our Mission</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Theatre as a Tool<br />for Social Change</h2>
      <div class="gold-divider"></div>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        We believe every play has the power to change a mind, and every changed mind 
        has the power to transform a community. Our work goes beyond the stage.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mission-cards">
      <div class="mission-card animate-in" data-delay="0">
        <div class="card-number">01</div>
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" width="28" height="28">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Gender Justice & Women's Rights</h3>
        <p>
          Productions like <em>Mera Kya Kasoor</em> — which won national acclaim at Rajrangam — 
          tackle female foeticide, gender discrimination, and the plight of the girl child. 
          Our plays have reached schools, rural communities, and urban audiences alike.
        </p>
        <div class="card-tag">Social Theatre</div>
      </div>

      <div class="mission-card animate-in" data-delay="1">
        <div class="card-number">02</div>
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" width="28" height="28">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
            <path d="M8.56 2.75c4.37 6.03 6.02 9.42 8.03 17.72m2.54-15.38c-3.72 4.35-8.94 5.66-16.88 5.85m19.5 1.9c-3.5-.93-6.63-.82-8.94 0-2.58.92-5.01 2.86-7.44 6.32"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Cultural Heritage & Identity</h3>
        <p>
          Rajasthani folk forms — Kuchipudi, Maach, Tamasha — are woven into our contemporary 
          productions. We document, celebrate, and revive traditional performance styles 
          that risk being lost to modernisation.
        </p>
        <div class="card-tag">Cultural Preservation</div>
      </div>

      <div class="mission-card animate-in" data-delay="2">
        <div class="card-number">03</div>
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" width="28" height="28">
            <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Civic Awareness & Democracy</h3>
        <p>
          From celebrating India's freedom struggle to staging plays about political 
          accountability and voter rights, ATR takes theatre into the heart of civic discourse, 
          making complex issues accessible to all.
        </p>
        <div class="card-tag">Civic Theatre</div>
      </div>

      <div class="mission-card animate-in" data-delay="3">
        <div class="card-number">04</div>
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" width="28" height="28">
            <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
            <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Youth Empowerment</h3>
        <p>
          Through the Actors Academy of Rajasthan, we train young artists in voice, 
          movement, direction, and dramaturgy — giving them tools not just for performance, 
          but for life and leadership.
        </p>
        <div class="card-tag">Education & Training</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="impact-bar animate-in">
      <div class="impact-item">
        <span class="impact-num">7</span>
        <span class="impact-label">Rajrangam Festivals Organised</span>
      </div>
      <div class="impact-sep"></div>
      <div class="impact-item">
        <span class="impact-num">40+</span>
        <span class="impact-label">Plays in Repertoire</span>
      </div>
      <div class="impact-sep"></div>
      <div class="impact-item">
        <span class="impact-num">15+</span>
        <span class="impact-label">National Theatre Groups Hosted</span>
      </div>
      <div class="impact-sep"></div>
      <div class="impact-item">
        <span class="impact-num">∞</span>
        <span class="impact-label">Stories Still to Tell</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .mission {
    background: var(--bg-alt);
    position: relative;
  }

  .mission::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--saffron), transparent);
    opacity: 0.25;
  }

  .mission-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .mission-header .gold-divider {
    margin: 1.5rem auto;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--saffron), transparent);
    width: 80px;
  }

  .mission-header .section-subtitle {
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .mission-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .mission-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: var(--transition);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .mission-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--saffron), var(--saffron-pale));
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transform-origin: left;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease;
    border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
  }

  .mission-card:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }

  .mission-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-strong);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  .card-number {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(232, 114, 12, 0.18);
    position: absolute;
    top: 1rem; right: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1;
    user-select: none;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .card-icon {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    background: var(--saffron-pale);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--saffron);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .mission-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .mission-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--ink-body);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .mission-card p em {
    color: var(--saffron);
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .card-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--saffron);
    background: var(--saffron-pale);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  /* Impact bar */
  .impact-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--saffron-pale), var(--bg-warm));
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .impact-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    text-align: center;
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 120px;
  }

  .impact-num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--saffron);
  }

  .impact-label {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .impact-sep {
    width: 1px;
    height: 50px;
    background: var(--border);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .mission-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .impact-bar { gap: 1.5rem; }
    .impact-sep { display: none; }
  }
</style>
